pullRequest.body:
Remove the condition of being equiv_invariant in IsFraisse
Deletions:
- IsFraisse.is_equiv_invariant

---
In the definition of `IsFraisse`, it was asked that the class is equivalence-invariant. However, this is already an easy consequence of two other properties: `IsFraisse.hereditary` and `IsFraisse.FG`. I don't see a reason to keep this, so I removed it from the definition, and I added the theorem `IsFraisse.is_equiv_invariant`. For the same reason, I removed a condition in the theorem `exists_cg_is_age_of`.
